==English==

From 22 to 26 August 2018 in Grenoble - France
During “the summer university of solidarity and rebel social movements and citizens” https://ue2018.org/

The CommonsCamp aims to create a meeting place for French and European activists, commoners and municipalists for the transition based on the commons. in France and Europe.

The intention is to offer a place and moments that allow us to develop 3 dimensions:

* '''LEARNING and CONTRIBUTING''' to the Grenoble’commons and municipalist experiences
* '''SHARE''' our initiatives for municipalities in France and Europe
* '''ORGANIZE''' the transition movement based on the commons

